                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "DPg7i",
                      "name": "ws4ContentP2",
                      "fill": "#0F172A",
                      "content": "We're building a banking layer on Solana that lets remote workers hold balances in USDC, EUR, GBP, KZT — receive transfers from employers, spend with a card, and off-ramp to local currencies without predatory fees.",
